15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 62.3, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 62.3. A. The Director of the Office of Management and
19 Enterprise Services shall promulgate rules for use by state agencies
20 and the Office of Management and Enterprise Services to dispose of
21 surplus property. The rules shall include standards for
22 recordkeeping, methods for removal or disposal of surplus property,
23 and acquisition by state agencies and authorized entities of surplus
24 property, and for Office management of surplus property programs.
